Class DevelopmentCard

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.DevelopmentCard
All Implemented Interfaces:
Production
Direct Known Subclasses:
DevelopmentCardStub, DevelopmentCardStub1
public class DevelopmentCard
extends java.lang.Object
implements Production
this class give access to all the information about a development card: resource cost, resources needed for development activation, benefits that can be generated thanks to its activation, victory points it generates, level and color.
